    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_liz-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……こんなに飲んだのはいつぶりかしら\nでも、夜はまだこれからよ。私についてこれる？",
      "startTime": 5.6569592975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "カッコ良く言っていますけどさっきからずっと酒を\n飲んでるだけですよ。その一杯で終わりにしましょう",
      "startTime": 14.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（今日は特別……とはいえ莉央さん、少し飲み過ぎだ）\n（もう少し前に止めておけば良かったな）",
      "startTime": 24,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "嫌よ、まだ貴方との夜は終わらないわ！　あら、いつの\n間にか貴方のグラスが空いてるわね。おかわりを――",
      "startTime": 32.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、その前に、ビーチに出てみませんか？\n莉央さんにしてほしいことがあるんです",
      "startTime": 40.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "してほしいこと？　もう外は真っ暗だけど……何かしら\nいいわよ、連れて行ってちょうだい",
      "startTime": 49.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "んー、空気が美味しい……。夜のビーチもいいわね\nあら？　こんな所にもテーブルがあるわ",
      "startTime": 62.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 33766.66793819999,
          "startTime": 88.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 53.6333356221
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 53.6333356221
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ……夜の砂浜の、オープンテラス席？\n洒落てるじゃない",
      "startTime": 70.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "このお店の名物なんですよ\n良かったらここで一休みしませんか？",
      "startTime": 74.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "いいわ。座りましょう\n……にぎやかな店内と違って、ここは静かね",
      "startTime": 80.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "聞こえるのは波の音だけ\nまるで、この世界に私達二人しかいないみたい",
      "startTime": 87.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "私達と、砂浜と波しかないわ。ふふっ……こんな風に\n何もない時間もいいわね。心が落ち着くわ",
      "startTime": 98.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "貴方がしてほしいことって、これだったの？",
      "startTime": 103.300007375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "はい。いつも多忙で気を張っている莉央さんだから\n何もしない時間を、過ごしてほしくて",
      "startTime": 110.3333358764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのね……。あら？　楽器の音が聞こえるわ\nこれは……三線？　沖縄の伝統楽器よね",
      "startTime": 119.8000025431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうです。この店のもう一つの名物が\n三線の店内ライブなんです",
      "startTime": 129.2000025431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "素敵なBGMも用意されてるなんて気が利いてる\nじゃない。いつまでだって、ここにいられそう",
      "startTime": 134.7558404242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "……素敵なプレゼントをありがとう\nねぇ、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 141.8000167846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "今晩はあともう一つだけ\n私のお願いを聞いてほしいの……いいかしら？",
      "startTime": 148.0333633422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい、マネージャーとして出来ることなら",
      "startTime": 152.766699473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……ぷっ、そういうところ、貴方らしいわね\n私のお願いはね……おかわりのドリンクがほしいの",
      "startTime": 162.3333633422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "今度は泡盛カクテルを飲みたいんだけど……\nメニューを見て、ずっと気になってたの。いいかしら？",
      "startTime": 169.8000300089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　なんだ、そんなことですか。いつもと\n少し雰囲気が違ったのでもっと難しいお願いかと",
      "startTime": 177.9333633422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこととは何よ。今日はもうだいぶ飲んでるでしょ\n飲み過ぎだって思ってない？",
      "startTime": 187.712570751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "た、確かに飲んでますが、最後に一杯くらいなら……\nもしもの時は俺がホテルまで連れて帰りますし",
      "startTime": 195.2333633422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "言ったわね？　それじゃ、最後にすごーく濃いのを\nもらうわ！　貴方にも付き合ってもらうわよ",
      "startTime": 204.0000300089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら、早くドリンクを持って来てちょうだい！\nあ、もちろん貴方の分も持って来るのよ？",
      "startTime": 211.4180952889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（……結局、宴は夜遅くまで続き）\n（翌日、莉央さんと俺は二日酔いになったのだった）",
      "startTime": 218.966682434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
